  "_comment": "Strategy prompt dispatch: maps the DecisionEngine action to the strategy prompt file injected at generation (read by StrategySelector). Paths are relative to the repo root. Purged 2026-07-23: content_type_mapping, category_paths, blog_to_category_mapping and eeat_levels were dead config from the old 5-level composer (targets no longer on disk, zero consumers in code); only strategy_prompts is read.",
